5|loc=\"Candy Harlots\"}}\n*[[Celtic Frost]] (''[[Cold Lake (album)|Cold Lake]]'' era)<ref>{{cite magazine|first= Ian |last= Christe |authorlink= Ian Christe |title= News |magazine= [[CMJ New Music Monthly]] |date= March 2000 |issue= 79 |page= 63 |issn= 1074-6978 |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=IyoEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA63&dq=%22glam%20metal%22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first= Aaron |last= Lariviere |title= The 40 Coolest NSFW Album Covers: Celtic Frost \u2013 \"I Won't Dance\" (1987) |date= 26 July 2012 |work= [[Stereogum]] |url= http://www.stereogum.com/1103951/the-40-coolest-nsfw-album-covers/franchises/list/attachment/olympus-digital-camera-7/ |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Child's Play (band)|Child's Play]]<ref name=\"Furious\"/>\n*[[Cinderella (band)|Cinderella]]<ref name=\"Furious\"/>{{sfn|Cogan|2011}}<ref name=\"Blender\"/><ref name=\"VH1-5\"/><ref name=\"About\">{{cite web|first= Chad |last= Bowar |title= Best Hair Metal Bands |publisher= About.com |url= http://heavymetal.about.com/od/toppicks/tp/hairbands.htm |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>{{sfn|Phillips|Cogan|2009|pp=52\u20133}}{{sfn|Christe|2003|loc=\"The Hollywood Glambangers\"|p=159}}{{sfn|Strother|2013|pp=99, 133}}\n*[[Circus of Power]]<ref>{{cite web|first= Alex |last= Henderson |title= Circus of Power \u2013 Vices |publisher= AllMusic |url= http://www.allmusic.com/album/vices-mw0000654475 |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Contraband (band)|Contraband]]{{sfn|Popoff|2014|p=205}}\n*[[Alice Cooper]] (late 1980s work)<ref name=\"VH1-3\"/>{{sfn|Popoff|2014|p=171}}\n*[[Cry Wolf (band)|Cry Wolf]]<ref name=\"Furious\"/>\n*[[Cycle Sluts from Hell]]<ref name=\"VH1-1\"/><ref name=\"Furious\"/><ref>{{cite web|first= Greg |last= Prato |title= Cycle Sluts from Hell \u2013 Artist Biography |publisher= AllMusic |url= http://www.allmusic.com/artist/cycle-sluts-from-hell-mn0000787285/biography |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n{{div col end}}\n\n===D===\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n*[[D.A.D. (band)|D.A.D.]]{