hard (band)|Gotthard]]<ref>{{cite web|first= Alexey |last= Eremenko |title= Gotthard \u2013 One Team One Spirit |publisher= AllMusic |url= http://www.allmusic.com/album/one-team-one-spirit-mw0000744063 |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Great White]]<ref name=\"VH1-4\"/><ref name=\"Furious\"/>{{sfn|Phillips|Cogan|2009|p=102}}\n*[[Guardian (band)|Guardian]]{{sfn|Strother|2013|p=41}}<ref>{{cite web|first= Paul |last= Gibson |title= Guardian Reality Show Experiment Has Begun |date= 16 April 2009 |publisher= Christian Rock 20 |url= http://www.thechristianrock20.com/guardian-reality-show-experiment-has-begun/ |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Guns N' Roses]]<ref name=\"Pop Metal\"/>{{sfn|Cogan|2011}}<ref name=\"Blender\"/><ref name=\"VH1-5\"/>{{sfn|Klypchak|2016}}{{sfn|Weinstein|2015|pp=223\u201326, 244\u201345}}{{sfn|Strother|2013|p=186}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n===H===\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n*[[Sammy Hagar]]<ref>{{cite web|first= Martin C. |last= Strong |authorlink= Martin C. Strong |title= Sammy Hagar Biography |url= http://thegreatrockbible.com/portfolio-item/sammy-hagar-biography/ |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Halloween (band)|Halloween]]<ref name=\"VH1-3\"/>\n*[[Hanoi Rocks]]{{sfn|Cogan|2011}}<ref name=\"VH1-5\"/>{{sfn|Christe|2003|loc=\"The Hollywood Glambangers\"|p=159}}{{sfn|Klypchak|2016}}{{sfn|Phillips|Cogan|2009|pp=108\u20139}}{{sfn|Popoff|2014|p=81}}\n*[[Hardline (band)|Hardline]]<ref name=\"VH1-1\"/><ref name=\"Furious\"/>\n*[[Harem Scarem]]<ref>{{cite web|first= Rob |last= Theakston |title= Harem Scarem \u2013 The Essentials |publisher= AllMusic |url= http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-essentials-mw0000708763 |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>{{sfn|Popoff|2014|p=208}}\n*[[Heart (band)|Heart]] (1985\u20131990)<ref>{{cite web|first= Shawn |last= MacComber |title= All Hail Hair Metal Heart |website= [[PopMatters]] |date= 4 August 2015 |accessdate= 7 March 2020 |url= https://www.popmatters.com/195860-all-hail-hair-metal-heart-2495502666.html}}</r