madam-x-mn0001009202 |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Magdallan]]{{sfn|Strother|2013|p=50}}\n*[[Manic Street Preachers]] (''[[Generation Terrorists]]'' era)<ref>{{cite web|first= Kayley |last= Kravitz |title= Archiving Pain: Richey Edwards disappeared 20 years ago, but his genius with the Manics lives on |website= Vanyaland |date= 30 January 2015 |accessdate= 14 May 2019 |url= https://vanyaland.com/2015/01/30/lyrical-preacher-richey-edwards-disappeared-20-years-ago-sunday-genius-lives/}}</ref>\n*[[Michael Monroe]]{{sfn|Popoff|2014|p=177}}\n*[[M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce]]{{sfn|Weinstein|2015|pp=223\u201326}}{{sfn|Witmer|2010|p=22}}{{sfn|Harrington|2002|p=392}}<ref name=\"Pop Metal\"/><ref name=\"Furious\"/>{{sfn|Cogan|2011}}<ref name=\"Blender\"/><ref name=\"VH1-5\"/><ref name=\"About\"/>{{sfn|Christe|2003|loc=\"The Hollywood Glambangers\"|p=159}}{{sfn|Klypchak|2016}}{{sfn|Strother|2013|pp=48, 91, 133, 186, 220}}\n*[[Montrose (band)|Montrose]] (''[[Mean (album)|Mean]]'' era)<ref>{{cite web|first= Martin C. |last= Strong |title= Montrose Biography |url= http://thegreatrockbible.com/portfolio-item/montrose-biography/ |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Mr. Big (American band)|Mr. Big]]<ref name=\"VH1-4\"/><ref name=\"Furious\"/>{{sfn|Popoff|2014|pp=171, 182, 202}}<ref>{{cite web|first= Andrew |last= Leahey |title= Mr. Big \u2013 What If |publisher= AllMusic |url= http://www.allmusic.com/album/what-if-mw0002087059 |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n{{div col end}}\n\n===N===\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n*[[Nasty Idols]]<ref>{{cite web|title= Nasty Idols \u2013 Artist Biography |publisher= AllMusic |accessdate= 16 July 2016 |url= http://www.allmusic.com/artist/nasty-idols-mn0000115885/biography}}</ref>\n*[[Vince Neil]] (''[[Exposed (Vince Neil album)|Exposed]]'' era)<ref>{{cite web|first= Johnny |last= Loftus |title= Vince Neil \u2013 Exposed |publisher= AllMusic |accessdate= 16 July 2016 |url= http://www.allmusic.com/artist/nasty-idols-mn0000115885/biography}}</ref>\n*