riah Heep (band)|Uriah Heep]] (''[[Equator (Uriah Heep album)|Equator]]'' era){{sfn|Phillips|Cogan|2009|p=246}}<ref>{{cite web|first= Martin C. |last= Strong |title= Uriah Heep Biography |url= http://thegreatrockbible.com/portfolio-item/uriah-heep-biography/ |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n{{div col end}}\n\n===V===\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n*[[Vain (band)|Vain]]<ref>{{cite web|title= Vain |publisher= No Life 'til Metal |url= http://www.nolifetilmetal.com/vain.html |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Van Halen]]<ref name=\"Pop Metal\"/>{{sfn|Strother|2013|p=186}}{{sfn|Weinstein|2015|pp=223\u201326, 244}}{{sfn|Phillips|Cogan|2009|p=253}}<ref>{{cite web|first= Martin C. |last= Strong |title= Van Halen Biography |url= http://thegreatrockbible.com/portfolio-item/van-halen-biography/ |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Vanadium (band)|Vanadium]] (late 80s work)<ref>{{cite web|first= Eduardo |last= Rivadavia |title= Vanadium \u2013 Artist Biography |publisher= AllMusic |url= http://www.allmusic.com/artist/vanadium-mn0001760926 |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Vandal (band)|Vandal]]<ref name=\"Ramirez\"/>\n*[[Vandenberg (band)|Vandenberg]] (''[[Alibi (Vandenberg album)|Alibi]]'' era)<ref>{{cite web|first= Rob |last= Theakston |title= Vandenberg \u2013 Alibi |publisher= AllMusic |url= http://www.allmusic.com/album/alibi-mw0000658648 |accessdate= 16 July 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Vinnie Vincent Invasion]]<ref name=\"VH1-3\"/>{{sfn|Popoff|2014|pp=111, 133, 147}}\n*[[Vixen (band)|Vixen]]{{sfn|Weinstein|2015|pp=223\u201326}}<ref name=\"VH1-4\"/>{{sfn|Strother|2013|p=99}}{{sfn|Popoff|2014|pp=33, 83, 154, 182, 190}}<ref>{{cite web|first= Alex |last= Henderson |title= Vixen \u2013 Artist Biography |publisher= AllMusic |accessdate= 16 July 2016 |url= http://www.allmusic.com/artist/vixen-mn0000222748/biography}}</ref>\n{{div col end}}\n\n===W===\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n*[[War Babies (band)|War Babies]]<ref name=\"Furious\"/>\n*[[Warlock (band)|Warlock]]<ref name=\"VH1-3\"/>