/1432227209.html|title=Xavi, the third man|work=[[Marca (newspaper)|Marca]] |date=21 May 2015|access-date=25 October 2017}}</ref>\n* [[FIFA World Player of the Year|FIFA World Player of the Year Third place]]: [[2009 FIFA World Player of the Year|2009]]\n* [[UEFA Champions League]] top assist provider: [[2008\u201309 UEFA Champions League|2008\u201309]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2009/statistics/index.html |title=UEFA Champions League 2008/09 - History - Statistics \u2013 UEFA.com |publisher=UEFA.com |access-date=25 October 2017}}</ref>\n* [[UEFA Club Football Awards|UEFA Club Midfielder of the Year]]: [[UEFA Champions League Best Midfielder|2008\u201309]]\n* [[IFFHS World's Best Playmaker]]: 2008, 2009, 2010, 2011<ref name=\"Former Results\">{{cite web|url=http://iffhs.de/former-results/|title=Former Results|publisher=IFFHS|accessdate=13 January 2016}}</ref>\n* [[Don Bal\u00f3n Award|La Liga Breakthrough Player of the Year]]: 1999\n* [[Don Bal\u00f3n Award|La Liga Spanish Player of the Year]]: 2005\n* [[Trofeo Alfredo Di St\u00e9fano]]: 2nd place 2010, 3rd place 2011\n* [[LFP Awards|La Liga Midfielder of the Year]]: 2009, 2010, 2011\n* [[FIFA World Cup awards#All-Star Team|FIFA World Cup Dream Team]]: [[2010 FIFA World Cup#Statistics|2010]]<ref>{{cite web  |url = https://www.fifa.com/newscentre/news/newsid=1274177/index.html | title = Spaniards dominate Dream Team | publisher = fifa.com | date = 15 July 2010 | accessdate = 5 September 2014}}</ref>\n* [[UEFA European Championship Teams of the Tournament|UEFA European Championship Team of the Tournament]]: [[UEFA Euro 2008#Awards|2008]], [[UEFA Euro 2012#Awards|2012]]\n* [[FIFPro#FIFA FIFPro World XI|FIFA FIFPro World XI]]: [[FIFPro World XI|2008]], [[FIFPro World XI|2009]], [[2010 FIFA Ballon d'Or#FIFA/FIFPro World XI|2010]], [[2011 FIFA Ballon d'Or#FIFA/FIFPro World XI|2011]], [[2012 FIFA Ballon d'Or#FIFA/FIFPro World XI|2012]], [[2013 FIFA Ballon d'Or#FIFA/FIFPro World XI|20